{
  "stem": "15938.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It wasn't like it is today.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, to us it was a big deal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The family came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some family came from out of town, out of town, probably the next village.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they baked a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And after shul everybody came to our house and had kiddish, and that was it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was-- but it was very-- I remember that time I was allowed to go to shul.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was very, very sad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just remember everybody is crying.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Because?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't even think they knew the reason, but they knew that there was probably the last bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was very, very, very hard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, you know, they tried to make it as jolly as possible for his sake.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But it was-- it was-- I can't even explain it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It wasn't tragic.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was just sad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't even know if my grandmother was there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I think she was there because traveling was already for Jews wasn't allowed and things were bad.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So that was-- that was the bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "In our family, it was quite a big thing because the direct family had no other sons.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So on my-- you know, my near aunt-- we had a lot of aunts and uncles, dozens and dozens.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But we were half brothers and half sisters.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the real connection was with this one aunt who lived in town.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They had no sons so this was the big event-- the first bar mitzvah in the family.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mammerstein.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Rose Mammerstein.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They owned mineral waters.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had mineral-- and they bottled them and exported them all over Europe.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was supposed to have been good for the stomach.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that's where I used to play and go.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
